			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">ATC activates only if the page request method is POST and the cookie &quot;bbas_pass_code&quot; is wrong. The pass code is a hash of the server name, server admin, user's browser identification string and the first three octets of the user IPs: REMOTE_ADDR','HTTP_VIA','HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR.
<br />

<br />
If you want to learn more, I can send the source code.<br />_________________<br />Oleg Parashchenko, bbAntiSpam
